examples.en: Racism and sexism are major social problems.

examples.en: Sexism still works against (=harms or causes problems for) women in many professions.

examples.en: The Eve of biblical legend was a temptress, thus initiating a lamentable theme in the history of sexism.
examples.ru: Ева в библейской легенде была искусительницей, таким образом положив начало плачевной истории сексизма.
